{"ja527:0.1":"Jataka ","ja527:0.2":"Pannasanipata ","ja527:0.3":"Nilinikavagga ","ja527:0.4":"2 Ummadantijataka ","ja527:1.1":"“Nivesanam kassa nudam sunanda, ","ja527:1.2":"Pakarena pandumayena guttam; ","ja527:1.3":"Ka dissati aggisikhava dure, ","ja527:1.4":"Vehayasam pabbataggeva acci. ","ja527:2.1":"Dhita nvayam kassa sunanda hoti, ","ja527:2.2":"Sunisa nvayam kassa athopi bhariya; ","ja527:2.3":"Akkhahi me khippamidheva puttho, ","ja527:2.4":"Avavata yadi va atthi bhatta”. ","ja527:3.1":"“Ahanhi janami janinda etam, ","ja527:3.2":"Matya ca petya ca athopi assa; ","ja527:3.3":"Taveva so puriso bhumipala, ","ja527:3.4":"Rattindivam appamatto tavatthe. ","ja527:4.1":"Iddho ca phito ca suvaddhito ca, ","ja527:4.2":"Amacco ca te annataro janinda; ","ja527:4.3":"Tassesa bhariyabhiparakassa, ","ja527:4.4":"Ummadanti namadheyyena raja”. ","ja527:5.1":"“Ambho ambho namamidam imissa, ","ja527:5.2":"Matya ca petya ca katam susadhu; ","ja527:5.3":"Tada hi mayham avalokayanti, ","ja527:5.4":"Ummattakam ummadanti akasi. ","ja527:6.1":"Ya punnamase migamandalocana, ","ja527:6.2":"Upavisi pundarikattacangi; ","ja527:6.3":"Dve punnamayo tadahu amannaham, ","ja527:6.4":"Disvana paravatarattavasinim. ","ja527:7.1":"Alarapamhehi subhehi vaggubhi, ","ja527:7.2":"Palobhayanti mam yada udikkhati; ","ja527:7.3":"Vijambhamana harateva me mano, ","ja527:7.4":"Jata vane kimpurisiva pabbate. ","ja527:8.1":"Tada hi brahati sama, ","ja527:8.2":"amuttamanikundala; ","ja527:8.3":"Ekaccavasana nari, ","ja527:8.4":"migi bhantavudikkhati. ","ja527:9.1":"Kadassu mam tambanakha suloma, ","ja527:9.2":"Bahamudu candanasaralitta; ","ja527:9.3":"Vattanguli sannatadhirakuttiya, ","ja527:9.4":"Nari upannissati sisato subha. ","ja527:10.1":"Kadassu mam kancanajaluracchada, ","ja527:10.2":"Dhita tiritissa vilaggamajjha; ","ja527:10.3":"Muduhi bahahi palissajissati, ","ja527:10.4":"Brahavane jatadumamva maluva. ","ja527:11.1":"Kadassu lakharasarattasucchavi, ","ja527:11.2":"Bindutthani pundarikattacangi; ","ja527:11.3":"Mukham mukhena upanamayissati, ","ja527:11.4":"Sondova sondassa suraya thalam. ","ja527:12.1":"Yadaddasam tam titthantim, ","ja527:12.2":"Sabbabhaddam manoramam; ","ja527:12.3":"Tato sakassa cittassa, ","ja527:12.4":"Navabodhami kancinam. ","ja527:13.1":"Ummadantimaham dattha, ","ja527:13.2":"amuttamanikundalam; ","ja527:13.3":"Na supami divarattim, ","ja527:13.4":"sahassamva parajito. ","ja527:14.1":"Sakko ce me varam dajja, ","ja527:14.2":"so ca labbhetha me varo; ","ja527:14.3":"Ekarattam dvirattam va, ","ja527:14.4":"bhaveyyam abhiparako; ","ja527:14.5":"Ummadantya ramitvana, ","ja527:14.6":"siviraja tato siyam”. ","ja527:15.1":"“Bhutani me bhutapati namassato, ","ja527:15.2":"Agamma yakkho idametadabravi; ","ja527:15.3":"Ranno mano ummadantya nivittho, ","ja527:15.4":"Dadami te tam paricarayassu”. ","ja527:16.1":"“Punna ca dhamse amaro na camhi, ","ja527:16.2":"Jano ca me papamidanca janna; ","ja527:16.3":"Bhuso ca tyassa manaso vighato, ","ja527:16.4":"Datva piyam ummadantim adattha”. ","ja527:17.1":"“Janinda nannatra taya maya va, ","ja527:17.2":"Sabbapi kammassa katassa janna; ","ja527:17.3":"Yam te maya ummadanti padinna, ","ja527:17.4":"Bhusehi raja vanatham sajahi”. ","ja527:18.1":"“Yo papakam kamma karam manusso, ","ja527:18.2":"So mannati mayida mannimsu anne; ","ja527:18.3":"Passanti bhutani karontametam, ","ja527:18.4":"Yutta ca ye honti nara pathabya. ","ja527:19.1":"Anno nu te koci naro pathabya, ","ja527:19.2":"Saddheyya lokasmi na me piyati; ","ja527:19.3":"Bhuso ca tyassa manaso vighato, ","ja527:19.4":"Datva piyam ummadantim adattha”. ","ja527:20.1":"“Addha piya mayha janinda esa, ","ja527:20.2":"Na sa mamam appiya bhumipala; ","ja527:20.3":"Gaccheva tvam ummadantim bhadante, ","ja527:20.4":"Sihova selassa guham upeti”. ","ja527:21.1":"“Na pilita attadukhena dhira, ","ja527:21.2":"Sukhapphalam kamma pariccajanti; ","ja527:21.3":"Sammohita vapi sukhena matta, ","ja527:21.4":"Na papakammanca samacaranti”. ","ja527:22.1":"“Tuvanhi mata ca pita ca mayham, ","ja527:22.2":"Bhatta pati posako devata ca; ","ja527:22.3":"Daso aham tuyha saputtadaro, ","ja527:22.4":"Yathasukham sami karohi kamam”. ","ja527:23.1":"“Yo issaromhiti karoti papam, ","ja527:23.2":"Katva ca so nuttasate paresam; ","ja527:23.3":"Na tena so jivati dighamayu, ","ja527:23.4":"Devapi papena samekkhare nam. ","ja527:24.1":"Annatakam samikehi padinnam, ","ja527:24.2":"Dhamme thita ye paticchanti danam; ","ja527:24.3":"Paticchaka dayaka capi tattha, ","ja527:24.4":"Sukhapphalanneva karonti kammam. ","ja527:25.1":"Anno nu te koci naro pathabya, ","ja527:25.2":"Saddheyya lokasmi na me piyati; ","ja527:25.3":"Bhuso ca tyassa manaso vighato, ","ja527:25.4":"Datva piyam ummadantim adattha”. ","ja527:26.1":"“Addha piya mayha janinda esa, ","ja527:26.2":"Na sa mamam appiya bhumipala; ","ja527:26.3":"Yam te maya ummadanti padinna, ","ja527:26.4":"Bhusehi raja vanatham sajahi”. ","ja527:27.1":"“Yo attadukkhena parassa dukkham, ","ja527:27.2":"Sukhena va attasukham dahati; ","ja527:27.3":"Yathevidam mayha tatha paresam, ","ja527:27.4":"Yo evam janati sa vedi dhammam. ","ja527:28.1":"Anno nu te koci naro pathabya, ","ja527:28.2":"Saddheyya lokasmi na me piyati; ","ja527:28.3":"Bhuso ca tyassa manaso vighato, ","ja527:28.4":"Datva piyam ummadantim adattha”. ","ja527:29.1":"“Janinda janasi piya mamesa, ","ja527:29.2":"Na sa mamam appiya bhumipala; ","ja527:29.3":"Piyena te dammi piyam janinda, ","ja527:29.4":"Piyadayino deva piyam labhanti”. ","ja527:30.1":"“So nunaham vadhissami, ","ja527:30.2":"attanam kamahetukam; ","ja527:30.3":"Na hi dhammam adhammena, ","ja527:30.4":"aham vadhitumussahe”. ","ja527:31.1":"“Sace tuvam mayha satim janinda, ","ja527:31.2":"Na kamayasi naravira settha; ","ja527:31.3":"Cajami nam sabbajanassa sibya, ","ja527:31.4":"Maya pamuttam tato avhayesi nam”. ","ja527:32.1":"“Adusiyance abhiparaka tvam, ","ja527:32.2":"Cajasi katte ahitaya tyassa; ","ja527:32.3":"Maha ca te upavadopi assa, ","ja527:32.4":"Na capi tyassa nagaramhi pakkho”. ","ja527:33.1":"“Aham sahissam upavadametam, ","ja527:33.2":"Nindam pasamsam garahanca sabbam; ","ja527:33.3":"Mametamagacchatu bhumipala, ","ja527:33.4":"Yathasukham sivi karohi kamam”. ","ja527:34.1":"“Yo neva nindam na panappasamsam, ","ja527:34.2":"Adiyati garaham nopi pujam; ","ja527:34.3":"Siri ca lakkhi ca apeti tamha, ","ja527:34.4":"Apo suvutthiva yatha thalamha”. ","ja527:35.1":"“Yam kinci dukkhanca sukhanca etto, ","ja527:35.2":"Dhammatisaranca manovighatam; ","ja527:35.3":"Urasa aham paccuttarissami sabbam, ","ja527:35.4":"Pathavi yatha thavaranam tasanam”. ","ja527:36.1":"“Dhammatisaranca manovighatam, ","ja527:36.2":"Dukkhanca nicchami aham paresam; ","ja527:36.3":"Ekovimam harayissami bharam, ","ja527:36.4":"Dhamme thito kinci ahapayanto”. ","ja527:37.1":"“Saggupagam punnakammam janinda, ","ja527:37.2":"Ma me tuvam antarayam akasi; ","ja527:37.3":"Dadami te ummadantim pasanno, ","ja527:37.4":"Rajava yanne dhanam brahmananam”. ","ja527:38.1":"“Addha tuvam katte hitesi mayham, ","ja527:38.2":"Sakha mamam ummadanti tuvanca; ","ja527:38.3":"Nindeyyu deva pitaro ca sabbe, ","ja527:38.4":"Papanca passam abhisamparayam”. ","ja527:39.1":"“Na hetadhammam siviraja vajjum, ","ja527:39.2":"Sanegama janapada ca sabbe; ","ja527:39.3":"Yam te maya ummadanti padinna, ","ja527:39.4":"Bhusehi raja vanatham sajahi”. ","ja527:40.1":"“Addha tuvam katte hitesi mayham, ","ja527:40.2":"Sakha mamam ummadanti tuvanca; ","ja527:40.3":"Satanca dhammani sukittitani, ","ja527:40.4":"Samuddavelava duraccayani”. ","ja527:41.1":"“Ahuneyyo mesi hitanukampi, ","ja527:41.2":"Dhata vidhata casi kamapalo; ","ja527:41.3":"Tayi huta raja mahapphala hi, ","ja527:41.4":"Kamena me ummadantim paticcha”. ","ja527:42.1":"“Addha hi sabbam abhiparaka tvam, ","ja527:42.2":"Dhammam acari mama kattuputta; ","ja527:42.3":"Anno nu te ko idha sotthikatta, ","ja527:42.4":"Dvipado naro arune jivaloke”. ","ja527:43.1":"“Tuvam nu settho tvamanuttarosi, ","ja527:43.2":"Tvam dhammagutto dhammavidu sumedho; ","ja527:43.3":"So dhammagutto cirameva jiva, ","ja527:43.4":"Dhammanca me desaya dhammapala”. ","ja527:44.1":"“Tadingha abhiparaka, ","ja527:44.2":"sunohi vacanam mama; ","ja527:44.3":"Dhammam te desayissami, ","ja527:44.4":"satam asevitam aham. ","ja527:45.1":"Sadhu dhammaruci raja, ","ja527:45.2":"sadhu pannanava naro; ","ja527:45.3":"Sadhu mittanamaddubbho, ","ja527:45.4":"papassakaranam sukham. ","ja527:46.1":"Akkodhanassa vijite, ","ja527:46.2":"thitadhammassa rajino; ","ja527:46.3":"Sukham manussa asetha, ","ja527:46.4":"sitacchayaya sanghare. ","ja527:47.1":"Na cahametam abhirocayami, ","ja527:47.2":"Kammam asamekkhakatam asadhu; ","ja527:47.3":"Ye vapi natvana sayam karonti, ","ja527:47.4":"Upama ima mayham tuvam sunohi. ","ja527:48.1":"Gavance taramananam, ","ja527:48.2":"jimham gacchati pungavo; ","ja527:48.3":"Sabba ta jimham gacchanti, ","ja527:48.4":"nette jimham gate sati. ","ja527:49.1":"Evameva manussesu, ","ja527:49.2":"yo hoti setthasammato; ","ja527:49.3":"So ce adhammam carati, ","ja527:49.4":"pageva itara paja; ","ja527:49.5":"Sabbam rattham dukham seti, ","ja527:49.6":"raja ce hoti adhammiko. ","ja527:50.1":"Gavance taramananam, ","ja527:50.2":"ujum gacchati pungavo; ","ja527:50.3":"Sabba gavi ujum yanti, ","ja527:50.4":"nette ujum gate sati. ","ja527:51.1":"Evameva manussesu, ","ja527:51.2":"yo hoti setthasammato; ","ja527:51.3":"So sace dhammam carati, ","ja527:51.4":"pageva itara paja; ","ja527:51.5":"Sabbam rattham sukham seti, ","ja527:51.6":"raja ce hoti dhammiko. ","ja527:52.1":"Na capaham adhammena, ","ja527:52.2":"amarattamabhipatthaye; ","ja527:52.3":"Imam va pathavim sabbam, ","ja527:52.4":"vijetum abhiparaka. ","ja527:53.1":"Yanhi kinci manussesu, ","ja527:53.2":"ratanam idha vijjati; ","ja527:53.3":"Gavo daso hirannanca, ","ja527:53.4":"vatthiyam haricandanam. ","ja527:54.1":"Assitthiyo ratanam manikanca, ","ja527:54.2":"Yancapi me candasuriya abhipalayanti; ","ja527:54.3":"Na tassa hetu visamam careyyam, ","ja527:54.4":"Majjhe sivinam usabhomhi jato. ","ja527:55.1":"Neta hita uggato ratthapalo, ","ja527:55.2":"Dhammam sivinam apacayamano; ","ja527:55.3":"So dhammamevanuvicintayanto, ","ja527:55.4":"Tasma sake cittavase na vatto”. ","ja527:56.1":"“Addha tuvam maharaja, ","ja527:56.2":"niccam abyasanam sivam; ","ja527:56.3":"Karissasi ciram rajjam, ","ja527:56.4":"panna hi tava tadisi. ","ja527:57.1":"Etam te anumodama, ","ja527:57.2":"yam dhammam nappamajjasi; ","ja527:57.3":"Dhammam pamajja khattiyo, ","ja527:57.4":"rattha cavati issaro. ","ja527:58.1":"Dhammam cara maharaja, ","ja527:58.2":"matapitusu khattiya; ","ja527:58.3":"Idha dhammam caritvana, ","ja527:58.4":"raja saggam gamissasi. ","ja527:59.1":"Dhammam cara maharaja, ","ja527:59.2":"puttadaresu khattiya; ","ja527:59.3":"…pe… ","ja527:60.1":"Dhammam cara maharaja, ","ja527:60.2":"mittamaccesu khattiya; ","ja527:60.3":"…pe… ","ja527:61.1":"Dhammam cara maharaja, ","ja527:61.2":"vahanesu balesu ca; ","ja527:61.3":"…pe… ","ja527:62.1":"Dhammam cara maharaja, ","ja527:62.2":"gamesu nigamesu ca; ","ja527:62.3":"…pe… ","ja527:63.1":"Dhammam cara maharaja, ","ja527:63.2":"ratthesu janapadesu ca; ","ja527:63.3":"…pe… ","ja527:64.1":"Dhammam cara maharaja, ","ja527:64.2":"samanabrahmanesu ca; ","ja527:64.3":"…pe… ","ja527:65.1":"Dhammam cara maharaja, ","ja527:65.2":"migapakkhisu khattiya; ","ja527:65.3":"…pe… ","ja527:66.1":"Dhammam cara maharaja, ","ja527:66.2":"dhammo cinno sukhavaho; ","ja527:66.3":"Idha dhammam caritvana, ","ja527:66.4":"raja saggam gamissasi. ","ja527:67.1":"Dhammam cara maharaja, ","ja527:67.2":"sainda deva sabrahmaka; ","ja527:67.3":"Sucinnena divam patta, ","ja527:67.4":"ma dhammam raja pamado”ti. ","ja527:68.1":"Ummadantijatakam dutiyam. "}